data.description: SELLER OFFERING $10,000 IN CONCESSIONS! Welcome to your dream home located in a prestigious gated community! Home has double door entryway and decorative high ceilings with a spacious layout and natural lighting.  Bedroom design arrangement is main bedroom situated on the opposite side from the other two bedrooms. Baths have spacious showers. All-tile flooring throughout home. Windows covered with custom rolling blinds.  Garage features a mini-split system for optimal temperature control and Epoxy floor coating. Water heater recently replaced. Front yard landscaping.  Privacy fence.    Seller offering $10,000 in Concessions. Storage Unit and Butane Gas Tank located in backyard as seen in photographs do not convey.
